{"tid":1280133,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（心理輔導）青草地全人發展中心","createTime":"2019-07-03T01:01:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T01:01:25.000Z","uid":42687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c3503ca7c0abad71de10245839e8ea57c1f83fd1","tid":1280133,"uid":42687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:01:25.000Z","msg":"代教徒朋友轉發，佢話好多年輕發過夢既教友呢排情緒都好激動，狂喊講唔到野，大家都好心痛。<br />\n有需要既巴絲，可以去搵人傾下。<br />\n<br />\n青草地全人發展中心<br />\n從4/7起直到另行通知為止，青草地在星期二、四早上10:00-12:00會開放給社工朋友或其他有需要的青年朋友來尋求支援，和彼此支援，我們也有輔導員駐場義務提供支援。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2740761302617945&amp;id=286962927997807\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2740761302617945%26id%3D286962927997807&d=ItsvLBlInL5d1alZeSWtsJE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=9f2ff1db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2740761302617945&amp;id=286962927997807</a>"}]}